{"tid":1686537,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【與撐警朋友割席】梁芷珊：冇餘力同你有共同話題","createTime":"2019-11-01T07:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:11:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80c3ee0f7396c1a5f15576bf4a3530b5122063d0","tid":1686537,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20191101/s00009/78135fe3bc7a59f353cc3f3e8351f49d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20191101%2Fs00009%2F78135fe3bc7a59f353cc3f3e8351f49d.jpg&h=1a42eda0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(fb)<br />\n<br />\n才女梁芷珊昨晚轉發了警察在蘭桂坊施放催淚彈，以及屯門逸生閣有多名市民被捕的新聞：她慨嘆：「今（昨）晚，又失眠。輾轉反側，終做了一件最軟弱無力嘅事：逐一去看facebook friends，今時今日仲係撐警的，仲係話無人犯法警察點會要執法嘅人，不做朋友了。我應該是，今生今世都沒有餘力，與你再有共同話題，或與你同一視覺。」<br />\n<br />\n梁芷珊亦在hashtag寫道：「#做朋友都係有今生無來世 #只會同正義良知做朋友 #有一個好似讀咗好多年法律老豆（竇）都係律師行partner嘅30歲律師仔 #有一個覺得自己溝死女晚晚蒲老蘭第二朝返工仲成身酒氣嘅偽CEO #有一個自稱女強人開agency幫人搵外傭的C（師）奶仔 #仲有好多 #繼續del」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191101/1572589103702/%E3%80%90%E8%88%87%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%91%E6%A2%81%E8%8A%B7%E7%8F%8A-%E5%86%87%E9%A4%98%E5%8A%9B%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191101%2F1572589103702%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E8%258A%25B7%25E7%258F%258A-%25E5%2586%2587%25E9%25A4%2598%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvM%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=bc4ea98c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191101%2F1572589103702%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25